<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>     
<body>
    <!-- Top Nav Bar -->
<!-- Top Nav Bar -->
<%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>     

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <main id="how-blood-donation-helps">  
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Why Donate Blood?</h2>
            <p>Blood donation is a simple act of kindness that can save lives. Each time you donate blood, you help hospitals provide critical care to patients in need.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Who Benefits -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Who Benefits from Blood Donations?</h2>
            <div class="content-container">
                <img src="path/to/patients-in-surgery.jpg" alt="Patients in Surgery" class="related-image">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h3>Patients in Surgery</h3>
                    <p>Blood is essential for surgeries, including those involving trauma, heart disease, and other medical conditions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content-container">
                <img src="path/to/trauma-patients.jpg" alt="Trauma Patients" class="related-image">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h3>Trauma Patients</h3>
                    <p>Accident victims and trauma patients often require immediate blood transfusions to replace lost blood.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content-container">
                <img src="path/to/cancer-patients.jpg" alt="Cancer Patients" class="related-image">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h3>Cancer Patients</h3>
                    <p>Many cancer treatments cause a reduction in blood cells, making transfusions necessary for recovery.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content-container">
                <img src="path/to/blood-disorders.jpg" alt="Blood Disorders" class="related-image">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h3>Patients with Blood Disorders</h3>
                    <p>Conditions like anemia and sickle cell disease often require regular blood transfusions to manage symptoms.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Statistics and Impact -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Statistics and Impact</h2>
            <p>Each donation can save up to three lives. The need for blood is constant, as every two seconds, someone in the world needs blood.</p>
            <img src="path/to/impact-statistics.jpg" alt="Blood Donation Impact Statistics" class="related-image">
        </section>

        <!-- Testimonials -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Testimonials</h2>
            <blockquote>
                "Donating blood was one of the best decisions I've made. Knowing that my donation could help save lives is an amazing feeling." – Jane Doe, blood donor
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote>
                "Receiving a blood transfusion during my treatment made all the difference. I'm grateful to all the donors." – John Smith, recipient
            </blockquote>
        </section>

        <!-- Community Impact -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>The Community Impact</h2>
            <p>Blood donation helps ensure a stable and diverse blood supply for all. It is a critical component of healthcare, aiding patients and communities alike.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Get Involved</h2>
            <p>Become a blood donor today. Your donation can make a difference. Check out upcoming blood drives or find a donation center near you.</p>
            <a href="donate-now.html" class="cta-button">Donate Now</a>
        </section>

    </main>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>     
        
    </body>
    </html>